# YouTube — Data API v3 via Google OAuth (confirmed in Vercel)
# OAuth flow: user visits /api/auth/google → Google consent → callback stores refresh_token in MongoDB
# At runtime: refresh_token is read from DB and exchanged for a fresh access_token
